<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yifanov" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5563061); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5563061&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224373" alt="Yifanov" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5563061)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yifanov" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5563061); return false;">Yifanov</a></span>：</strong>不知道大家怎么想，反正我是受不了云小鬼</p>
