<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/universe647" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4376536); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4376536&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224373" alt=" Universe647" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4376536)" /></a> <a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/universe647" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4376536); return false;">Universe647</a></span>：</strong>曝光世界观？</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/macro-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6357357); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6357357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224373" alt="Macro Z" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6357357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/macro-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6357357); return false;">Macro Z</a></span>：</strong>虽然想想还不错，不过总觉得跟基金会的精神相悖。混沌分裂者倒是可以，但就提不上护送了。</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/misaya1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5393648); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5393648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224373" alt="Misaya1" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5393648)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/misaya1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5393648); return false;">Misaya1</a></span>：</strong>屑六会喜欢的（bushi）</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/forty-nine49" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4465756); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4465756&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224373" alt="Forty-nine49" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4465756)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/forty-nine49" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4465756); return false;">Forty-nine49</a></span>：</strong>基金会的人不会干这种事吧？</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drstevenxu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6326265); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6326265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224373" alt="DrStevenXu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6326265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drstevenxu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6326265); return false;">DrStevenXu</a></span>：</strong>剧情过于出乎意料啊这 堪称基金会爽文</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jwhdetd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6330489); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6330489&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224373" alt="JWHDETD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6330489)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jwhdetd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6330489); return false;">JWHDETD</a></span>：</strong>同感，云小鬼确实令人不怎么好受</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/durot" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3164731); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3164731&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224373" alt="Durot" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3164731)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/durot" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3164731); return false;">Durot</a></span>：</strong>虽然但是，我觉得这篇至少应该存在（</p>
</blockquote>
