<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-ful" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4959716); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4959716&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224373" alt="Dr Ful" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4959716)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-ful" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4959716); return false;">Dr Ful</a></span></p>
