</div>
<div id="u-credit-00005-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/higashikatajosuke" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6150792); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6150792&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224373" alt="HigashikataJosuke" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6150792)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/higashikatajosuke" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6150792); return false;">HigashikataJosuke</a></span></p>
