<div id="u-credit-00086-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zgyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6225762); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6225762&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610224374" alt="ZGYN" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6225762)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zgyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6225762); return false;">ZGYN</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1600563029 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">20 Sep 2020 00:50</span></p>
</div>
